snippet.title: Mario and Sonic at the Rio 2016 Olympic Games - Heroes Showdown (Wii U)
snippet.description:
Mario and Sonic at the Rio 2016 Olympic Games Heroes Showdown Gameplay (Wii U)

Playthrough of Heroes Showdown in Mario & Sonic at the Rio 2016 Olympic Games for the Nintendo Wii U. In this mode you can play with Team Mario or Team Sonic in knockout rounds, you win when you have knocked out Mario or Sonic. Below is a playlist with all of my gameplay videos and compilations for this game

Mario and Sonic at the Rio 2016 Olympic Games Playlist:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLN_ilAf6ExtJlB8DdOW2q43fjus8Zp20O
